<p><a name="1.6"><b>1.6 How to Order the Service Pack&nbsp;6 CD </b></a></p>
<p>The Windows&nbsp;NT&nbsp;4.0 Service Pack CD contains supplemental and support files that you may find useful. To order the CD, visit the Microsoft Windows&nbsp;NT Server Web site at:<br>
